flowRoot.flowPara: User inputs Gene IDs in text box or selects a CSV file with a column labeled "tair_locus"
[OPTIONAL] User downloads a template annotation file, fills in the columns and uploads it
User clicks the submit button below the method used to input gene IDs
The application processes the data for the selected genes
User selects parameters specific to the visualization in that tab
The application processes and displays the data per the users parameters
User clicks the download button located above any table:
System dialog appears to download the table as a .csv file to the user's comupter
